items.title: Awesome Rtc
items.content_text:
### Server Software / SIP Servers

*   [Flexisip (‚≠ê167)](https://github.com/BelledonneCommunications/flexisip) - SIP server suite comprising proxy, presence and group chat functions.

### Developer Resources / Rust Libraries

*   [libsip](https://docs.rs/libsip/0.2.4/libsip) - SIP implementation, with a focus towards softphone clients.
*   [sipcore (‚≠ê31)](https://github.com/armatusmiles/sipcore) - Rust framework for creating SIP applications.
*   [rtcrs/webrtc (‚≠ê4.6k)](https://github.com/rtcrs/webrtc) - WebRTC stack, supporting SDP, RTP, RTCP and SRTP.

### Developer Resources / Dart Libraries

*   [dart-sip-ua (‚≠ê358)](https://github.com/cloudwebrtc/dart-sip-ua) - Dart-lang port of JsSIP, capable of SIP over WebSocket.
